🏦 Mini Bank System (C Language)

📌 Overview

This is a simple Mini Bank System built using the C programming language.
It simulates basic banking operations like account creation, deposit, withdrawal, and balance checking.

---

🚀 Features

- 🆕 Create Account
- 💰 Deposit Money
- 💸 Withdraw Money
- 📊 Check Balance
- 🔁 Menu-driven interface

---

🛠️ Technologies Used

- C Programming Language
- Standard Input/Output ("stdio.h")

---


